counter.cpu.coreUtilization.label="Core 利用率"
counter.cpu.coreUtilization.summary="CPU 利用率 的 corresponding core (if hyper-threading is 已启用) as a 百分比 during the 间隔 (A core is utilized if either or both of its 日志ical CPUs are utilized)"
