counter.cpu.utilization.PCORE.label="CORE UTIL(%)"
counter.cpu.utilization.PCORE.summary="The 百分比 of CPU cycles per core when at least one 的 PCPUs in this core is unhalted. It's the reverse 的 core IDle, which 是 百分比 of CPU cycles when all PCPUs in this core are halted. Effectively, equal to CPU.利用率 per PCPU when hyper-threading 不 已用"
counter.cpu.utilization.PCPU.label="PCPU UTIL(%)"
counter.cpu.utilization.PCPU.summary="The 百分比 of unhalted CPU cycles per physical CPU"
counter.cpu.wait.label="Wait"
