counter.cpu.wait.RESPOOL.label="%WAIT"
counter.cpu.wait.RESPOOL.summary="This 是 总计 wait time (百分比 denormalized from 0% up to 100xNumWorlds%). I.e., the 资源池 / scheduling 组 is waiting for some VMKernel 资源. This wait time includes I/O wait time, IDle time 和 among other 资源"
